OL,3,CCounter terror police assess claims
OL,4,CChina forced uni to drop research
OL,6,FCounter terror police are assessing
OL,7,Fpotential national security issues
OL,8,Fafter a university professor was
OL,9,Fallegedly ordered to stop research
OL,10,Finto human rights abuses in China.
OL,12,FSheffield Hallam University has faced
OL,13,Fclaims it bowed to pressure from
OL,14,FChina's authorities after it
OL,15,Fdiscontinued Prof Laura Murphy's
OL,16,Finvestigation into a series of reports
OL,17,Fabout the government's treatment of
OL,18,Fpeople in the Uyghur region.
