OL,4,CChina forced uni to drop research
OL,6,FThe university said the decision was
OL,7,F"not based on commercial interests in
OL,8,FChina".
OL,10,FBut lawyers acting for Prof Murphy
OL,11,Fsaid documents obtained from the
OL,12,Funiversity showed it happened after
OL,13,Fdirect threats from Chinese state
OL,14,Fsecurity.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Counter Terrorism
OL,17,FPolicing (CTP) London confirmed it had
OL,18,Freceived a referral from South
OL,19,FYorkshire Police relating to
OL,20,F"potential National Security Act
OL,21,Fallegations".
