OL,4,CChina forced uni to drop research
OL,6,FThey added: "The details of the
OL,7,Fallegation are now in the process of
OL,8,Fbeing assessed by specialist officers
OL,9,Fwithin CTP London to determine whether
OL,10,Fthere are any possible offences and if
OL,11,Fany further police action or
OL,12,Finvestigation is therefore required."
OL,14,FProf Murphy said she was told her work
OL,15,Fon China had been dropped by the
OL,16,Funiversity after returning from a
OL,17,Fcareer break in early 2025.
