OL,6,FShe told the BBC the university had
OL,7,Ftold her it had decided not to
OL,8,Fcontinue with her research due to "the
OL,9,Fcorporate insurance position" and "our
OL,10,Fduty of care to colleagues working in
OL,11,Fboth China and the UK".
OL,13,FIt followed allegations Chinese
OL,14,Fauthorities were "intimidating and
OL,15,Fharassing and interrogating the staff
OL,16,Fthat the university has in Beijing",
OL,17,Fthe professor said.
