OL,6,FLeigh Day Solicitors said documents
OL,7,Fobtained from the university showed
OL,8,FChina had blocked Sheffield Hallam
OL,9,FUniversity's access to the internet in
OL,10,FChina in response to publications from
OL,11,Fthe Forced Labour Lab, an initiative
OL,12,Fat the university's Helena Kennedy
OL,13,FCentre.
OL,15,FProf Murphy said she had seen proof
OL,16,Fthe university had traded her academic
OL,17,Ffreedom for access to the Chinese
OL,18,Fstudent market.
