OL,6,FBoth the university and the Chinese
OL,7,Fgovernment has rejected the
OL,8,Faccusations.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Sheffield Hallam
OL,11,Fsaid its decision not to continue with
OL,12,FProfessor Murphy's research was taken
OL,13,F"based on our understanding of a
OL,14,Fcomplex set of circumstances at the
OL,15,Ftime, including being unable to secure
OL,16,Fthe necessary professional indemnity
OL,17,Finsurance".
