OL,6,FThe university added that the decision
OL,7,F"was not based on commercial interest
OL,8,Fin China" and that China was not a
OL,9,Fsignificant international student
OL,10,Fmarket for the university.
OL,12,FThe university had since apologised
OL,13,Fand committed to supporting the
OL,14,Fprofessor's research.
OL,16,FThe spokesperson said: "Following a
OL,17,Freview, we have since approved
OL,18,FProfessor Murphy's latest research and
OL,19,Fare committed to supporting her to
OL,20,Fundertake and disseminate this
OL,21,Fimportant work.
