OL,11,FA Government spokesperson said: "Any
OL,12,Fattempt by a foreignstate to
OL,13,Fintimidate, harass or harm individuals
OL,14,Fin theUKwill not be tolerated, and
OL,15,Fthe Government has made this clear to
